         qml-module-qtquick-dialogs
Description: mathematics based puzzle game 
 2048 puzzle is mathematics based puzzle game where you have to merge
 the similar number tiles (2n) by moving the arrow keys in four 
 different directions. When two tiles with the same number touch, 
 they will merge into one
